Delayed transition: a literal-millisecond `after` timer fires on virtual-time
advance and lands in a top-level final state.
-- machine.json --
{
  "id": "t",
  "initial": "wait",
  "states": {
    "wait": {
      "after": {
        "1000": { "target": "#go" }
      }
    },
    "go": { "type": "final" }
  }
}
-- scenario --
expect active wait
advance 1s
expect active go
expect status done
